author: Divya Rao
title: Photo: Rannvijay Singha Out On A Special Date With His Wife
text:
A post shared by Rannvijay (@rannvijaysingha) on Feb 13, 2017 at 9:54pm PST 
Ranvijay Singha and his wife, Prianka Singha , just welcomed a beautiful baby girl, Kainaat , into their lives about a month ago, and the doting father has been spending lots of time with her. Firstly, can we just take a minute to talk about how beautiful and thoughtful that name is? We love it! Rannvijay shared a lovely photo of his wife and him on a date sans Kainaat… and it’s too cute. A post shared by Rannvijay (@rannvijaysingha) on Mar 2, 2017 at 2:10am PST 
Awww! Got to love how cute these two are! 0
